{"tid":2516740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"染疫泰國台商坦承「假陰性證明」是自製 最高罰15萬","createTime":"2021-05-05T00:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T08:35:47.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e78824b9aa8104b68bd28e65df554aa2be6c5520","tid":2516740,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"染疫泰國台商坦承「假陰性證明」是自製 最高罰15萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2021-05-04 20:15 聯合報 記者蕭羽耘／台北即時報導<br />\n<br />\n中央流行疫情指揮中心昨新增六例境外移入案例，其中包含二日自泰國搭乘長榮航空，持陰性證明返台的50多歲台商（案1149），泰國北柳府一日通報我國駐泰代表處，我國有一名確診患者，使他持造假核酸檢測陰性證明東窗事發，台商已向指揮中心坦承假證明是自己做的，指揮中心將先依傳染病防治法，最高15萬罰鍰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/120940/5433668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F120940%2F5433668&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=89cec7dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/120940/5433668</a>"},{"pid":"8d965c65d31dee47efbfa86dc92b58fcfb81da8b","tid":2516740,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:38:40.000Z","msg":"赴台「陰性證明」如造假 最多要罰這麼多錢<br />\n<br />\n2020-11-29 17:09 記者楊雅棠、邱宜君／台北報導<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">台灣出現持有陰性證明入境的印尼移工變成確診者，且類似個案層出不窮，外界質疑，相關證明可能造假，對此，台疫情指揮中心表示，確實有此可能，且很難避免</span></strong>，12月1日起入境台灣均須攜帶三日內核酸檢驗陰性報告，歡迎民眾檢舉，如調查證明造假，將依傳染病防治法開罰新台幣1萬元至15萬元。(約350美元至5260美元)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.worldjournal.com/wj/amp/story/121475/5053732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Famp%2Fstory%2F121475%2F5053732&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=10401a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.worldjournal.com/wj/amp/story/121475/5053732</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣仲未淪陷？"},{"pid":"5b797016e60635159b855dad946247e78f7521e9","tid":2516740,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:40:04.000Z","msg":"如果無病點解要做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1b753f364fe6ca78ac88805613c15738c9bc6e","tid":2516740,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b797016e60635159b855dad946247e78f7521e9","tid":2516740,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:40:04.000Z","msg":"如果無病點解要做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:02:57.000Z","msg":"真係去驗<br />\n驗到陽性就走唔到"},{"pid":"304006cba4190ece99530d78f096be26f0893851","tid":2516740,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}